                <li class="dropdown">
                  <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-plus"></i> 新闻抽取 <span class="caret"></span></a>
                  <ul class="dropdown-menu" role="menu">
                    <li class="dropdown-header">新闻网站选取</li>
                    <li><a href="scrapy_pp">澎湃新闻</a></li>
                    <li><a href="scrapy_bj">新京报网</a></li>
                    <li><a href="scrapy_nf">南方周末</a></li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li class="dropdown">
                  <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-plus"></i> 新闻聚类 <span class="caret"></span></a>
                  <ul class="dropdown-menu" role="menu">
                    <li class="dropdown-header">聚类算法选取</li>
                        <li><a href="cluster">基于k均值的层次凝聚聚类算法</a></li>
                    <li class="dropdown-header">话题抽取</li>
                        <li class="active1"><a href="keyhots">聚类关键字提取及热力值计算</a></li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
                <li class="dropdown">
                  <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown"><i class="fa fa-fw fa-plus"></i> 历史任务 <span class="caret"></span></a>
